Iga '''Azuknni''' yan wanaw n [[Tuga]] d imɣan lli bahra ilan atig dar isusiyn d iclḥiyn. iga yan ɣ imɣan lli s iqqan d ad yili ɣ kraygat tigmmi acku irwa i tmuḍan tikuyassanin.

Nẓḍar at nsu ayiwan nɣt nsmun d [[Akʷfay|ukʷfay]]. Irwa i uzbbaṛ n wakur d akud nna nmlalli.

